So if you're not doing
the Training Box project,

81
00:05:30,020 --> 00:05:31,260
are you going back to Hong Kong, China?

82
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:34,740
Not immediately.

83
00:05:35,620 --> 00:05:36,900
I have some things to take care of.

84
00:05:38,220 --> 00:05:38,860
What things?

85
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:42,140
Have you sold

86
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,180
all the backlogged materials?

87
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:48,460
Not yet.

88
00:05:49,860 --> 00:05:51,340
I approached several buyers at once.

89
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:53,900
But their offers are too low.

90
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,420
I'm still working on it.

91
00:05:58,700 --> 00:05:59,340
What's up?

92
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:00,540
Let's collaborate.

93
00:06:02,140 --> 00:06:03,740
I'll connect you with buyers.

94
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:05,340
After all these years

95
00:06:05,340 --> 00:06:06,540
in the securities company,

96
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:07,820
I've built some decent connections.

97
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:09,980
Deal.

98
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:13,380
Since we've known each other

99
