for so many years, can you go easy

100
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:16,420
on the consulting fee?

101
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:19,860
I'll think about it.

102
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:22,620
Come on, I'm in such a tough spot.

103
00:06:22,620 --> 00:06:23,980
You'd really charge me?

104
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:25,100
Absolutely.

105
00:06:25,460 --> 00:06:27,300
Don't you remember? I'm a money-grubber.

106
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:28,060
Funny.

107
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:30,060
So am I now.

108
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,180
Wish a pleasant cooperation with you.

109
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:34,780
Me too.

110
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:36,980
Yeah, look at these cherry tomatoes.

111
