Yeah, amazing.

114
00:06:41,420 --> 00:06:42,580
I knew you'd like it.

115
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:44,700
Try this one then.

116
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:46,500
Try this.

117
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:48,820
Ding Zhitong.

118
00:06:57,580 --> 00:06:58,180
Does it taste good?

119
00:06:58,580 --> 00:06:59,540
Yeah, delicious.

120
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:11,940
Alright, spill. When did you two start?

121
00:07:12,700 --> 00:07:14,580
Just a couple days ago.

122
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:17,100
Wang Yi,

123
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:18,700
did I do something wrong?

124
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:19,780
Why are you treating me like this?

125
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:21,860
No, it's just that we...

126
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:22,460
I'm not asking you.

127
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:23,620
Answer me!

128
00:07:24,220 --> 00:07:24,820
Gan Yang.

129
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,420
How could they do this to me?

130
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:29,500
What do they mean?

131
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:31,100
Seriously, what do they mean?

132
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:32,620
Enough!

133
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,140
We just didn't tell you

134
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:35,100
