137
00:07:39,780 --> 00:07:40,340
Exactly.

138
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:43,300
Shouldn't you be... happy for us?

139
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:46,260
My two closest friends

140
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:47,340
are dating behind my back.

141
00:07:47,940 --> 00:07:49,260
How would you feel if it were you?

142
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:51,620
- We...
- We...

143
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:52,300
Would you be mad?

144
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:53,020
Yes.

145
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:53,820
Would you?

146
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:55,300
Would you?

147
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:57,460
- We...
- We...

148
00:07:57,460 --> 00:07:58,220
You what?

149
00:08:01,260 --> 00:08:01,780
Yeah.

150
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,620
We're together now.

151
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:04,460
We're dating.

152
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,420
What are you gonna do about it?

153
