That's right.

154
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:08,140
What are you gonna do about it?

155
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:17,420
Fine.

156
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:19,100
Waiter!

157
00:08:19,700 --> 00:08:20,900
Two portions

158
00:08:20,940 --> 00:08:21,700
