160
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:23,340
All of them?

161
00:08:23,340 --> 00:08:24,420
All of them. Put it on their tab!

162
00:08:24,700 --> 00:08:25,420
Alright.

163
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:27,140
Wait, all of them...

164
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:27,500
Hey.

165
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:28,300
Yeah. Two portions of everything.

166
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:29,660
Can you two even finish all that?

167
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:30,340
None of your business.

168
00:08:32,060 --> 00:08:33,020
Alright, okay.

169
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:33,580
Fine.

170
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:34,900
As long as you're happy.

171
00:08:35,260 --> 00:08:35,980
You're laughing?

172
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:37,220
Whatever makes you happy.

173
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:37,900
You're laughing too?

174
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:41,060
What do you mean by this?

175
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:45,940
Now you're kissing?

176
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:47,220
Do it again.

177
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,660
Do it again. I dare you!

178
00:08:49,180 --> 00:08:49,820
Alright.

179
00:08:49,980 --> 00:08:50,700
Still kissing?

180
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:51,220
Stop it.

181
00:08:51,660 --> 00:08:52,380
Stop watching.

182
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:53,380
Let's not watch this.

183
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:54,220
Out of sight, out of mind.

184
00:08:54,220 --> 00:08:55,100
It's okay. Stop watching this.

185
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:56,220
Out of sight, out of mind.

186
00:08:57,020 --> 00:08:58,020
Oh come on, you two.

187
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:03,400
[LT Capital]

188
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:16,400
[Gan Yang]

189
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:19,400
[Wang Sen]

190
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,580
Mr. Wang, congratulations
on getting what you wanted

191
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,100
and securing Training Box.

192
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:35,700
Mr. Gan, thanks for your concession.

193
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:38,580
Hope you won't regret your decision.

194
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:39,780
Don't worry.

195
00:09:40,980 --> 00:09:42,300
I'd never let go

196
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:44,900
of what truly matters to me.

197
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:51,260
Funny.

198
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:55,900
I always get what I want.

199
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:08,660
Sir,

200
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:10,580
I've contacted all the companies

201
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:11,540
Ms. Ding reached out to.

202
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:13,940
They've agreed not to purchase
LT's materials.

203
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:15,620
Got it.

204
00:10:16,260 --> 00:10:16,860
Sir,

205
00:10:16,860 --> 00:10:19,020
there's one thing I don't quite get.

206
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,740
You're wondering

207
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:23,340
why I'm still targeting LT

208
00:10:23,740 --> 00:10:25,260
after they withdrew from Training Box

209
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,700
and had no further involvement
with Wang's?

210
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:28,620
Yes.

211
00:10:29,500 --> 00:10:30,620
Do you know

212
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:33,020
why Gan Yang left Ding Zhitong
seven years ago?

213
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:35,860
Because his company owed 200 million

214
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:37,100
and was on the verge of bankruptcy.

215
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:38,500
If...

216
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:42,700
I put him in the same position
as seven years ago,

217
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:43,740
no...

218
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:48,060
