219
00:10:50,180 --> 00:10:51,500
what choice do you think he'll make?

220
00:10:52,060 --> 00:10:52,780
I see.

221
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:54,940
He left her once.

222
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:56,420
He'll do it again.

223
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,300
I'm leaving.

224
00:11:03,420 --> 00:11:06,620
These companies seem
to have coordinated.

225
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,980
