00:13:51,020 --> 00:13:51,900
Yeah, why is this happening?

294
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,540
I understand your concerns.

295
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:56,500
Whether you choose to go or not

296
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:58,420
is entirely up to you.

297
00:14:01,020 --> 00:14:01,740
Should we go?

298
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,180
We promise that everyone

299
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:08,180
who goes will have their salary
and benefits unchanged.

300
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:09,900
But my family is all in Shanghai.

301
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:10,660
What if we don't go?

302
00:14:11,620 --> 00:14:12,380
Those who stay

303
00:14:13,140 --> 00:14:14,500
will receive severance packages.

304
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:16,860
And we'll provide recommendation letters

305
00:14:17,420 --> 00:14:18,940
and help place everyone
at other companies.

306
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:29,700
Please raise your hand if you're willing
to move to Putian with us.

307
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:42,460
Don't feel pressured.

308
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:43,820
Whatever you decide,

309
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:46,500
we'll respect it.

310
00:14:58,580 --> 00:14:59,180
I'll go.

311
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:05,140
Me too.

312
00:15:05,580 --> 00:15:17,260
- I'm in.
- Count me in.

313
00:15:41,020 --> 00:15:42,340
Thank you for your trust.

314
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:43,820
I promise

315
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:45,140
we'll return to Shanghai

316
00:15:46,940 --> 00:15:48,340
within a year.

317
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:52,620
- Great!
- Splendid!

318
00:15:58,180 --> 00:16:04,780
- Come on!
- Come on!

319
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:06,860
We can do it.

320
00:16:06,860 --> 00:16:08,540
- We can do it.
- Come on!

321
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:21,380
Thank you for your support.

322
00:16:22,100 --> 00:16:22,700
In the next few days,

323
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:24,500
let's pack up

324
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:25,860
and prepare to move to Putian.

325
00:16:26,900 --> 00:16:28,660
Just let me know if you need any help.

326
00:16:29,420 --> 00:16:33,020
Let's make this work in Putian!

327
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:36,860
- Alright!
- Alright!

328
00:16:36,860 --> 00:16:39,300
- Let's kill it!
- Let's kill it!

329
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:42,020
- Come on!
- Come on!

330
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:44,740
- Give it your all!
- Go!

331
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:58,600
[Matching Tech]

332
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:09,500
Why are you here?

333
00:17:09,860 --> 00:17:10,500
Coming to see me?

334
00:17:11,140 --> 00:17:11,660
Where are you going?

335
00:17:12,100 --> 00:17:12,620
I'll go with you.

336
00:17:13,060 --> 00:17:13,780
No, thanks.

337
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:15,300
What I'm going to do is pretty wild.

338
00:17:15,780 --> 00:17:16,740
You sure you want in?

339
00:17:17,300 --> 00:17:18,060
Absolutely.

340
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:19,340
Bring it on.

341
00:18:25,140 --> 00:18:27,100
Hello, a glass of water, please.

342
00:18:28,020 --> 00:18:28,740
Hey beautiful,

343
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:30,260
I've been watching you all night.

344
00:18:31,460 --> 00:18:33,140
May I have the honor
of having a drink with you?

345
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:34,060
Sure.

346
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:34,980
Cheers.

347
00:18:36,460 --> 00:18:37,060
Sorry.

348
00:18:37,260 --> 00:18:38,020
She doesn't drink.

349
00:18:38,900 --> 00:18:40,020
What are you doing?

350
00:18:40,380 --> 00:18:41,420
I'm not done having fun yet.

351
00:18:41,420 --> 00:18:42,420
I booked the whole place.

352
00:18:42,780 --> 00:18:43,660
Let me dance some more.

353
00:18:45,980 --> 00:18:47,060
Where are you taking me?

354
00:18:51,380 --> 00:18:52,780
Hey, what are you doing?

355
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,540
I'm not done having fun yet.

356
00:18:54,540 --> 00:18:55,660
I want to go back and have fun.

357
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:56,460
Mingmei,

358
00:18:56,780 --> 00:18:58,060
you're not actually enjoying this.

359
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:00,780
Everyone else is having a blast,

360
00:19:00,900 --> 00:19:01,860
but you're not happy at all.

361
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:03,020
I am.

362
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:05,180
Remember what I told you last time?

363
00:19:06,100 --> 00:19:06,900
Yes.

364
00:19:08,300 --> 00:19:09,500
You said you regretted it.

365
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:11,420
What?

366
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:14,060
You regret not stopping me
six years ago?

367
00:19:15,340 --> 00:19:15,900
No.

368
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:19,700
Then what?

369
00:19:23,580 --> 00:19:26,380
At the airport back then,

370
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:29,700
I wanted to tell you I'd wait for you.

371
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:34,260
But in the end, I didn't say anything.

372
00:19:39,380 --> 00:19:41,180
I've never regretted letting you go.

373
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:44,100
I wanted you
to become who you always wanted to be.

374
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:49,540
If I had another chance,

375
00:19:52,060 --> 00:19:53,100
I'd tell you

376
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:56,020
I'd wait for you forever.

377
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:00,540
No matter what happens,

378
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:03,780
I'll always be there for you.

379
00:20:04,820 --> 00:20:05,540
You...

380
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:09,460
So don't be afraid.

381
00:20:11,660 --> 00:20:13,100
I know about your illness

382
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:16,380
and have already contacted the doctor.

383
00:20:50,540 --> 00:20:52,300
This ring was made just for you.

384
00:20:54,620 --> 00:20:55,580
Three diamonds.

385
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:57,220
The main one is you,

386
00:20:57,940 --> 00:21:00,420
and the two little purple ones
are me and Yulin.

387
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:02,540
We'll always be with you.

388
00:21:05,780 --> 00:21:07,300
We'll always be there for you.

389
00:21:27,420 --> 00:21:28,180
Song Mingmei.

390
00:21:33,740 --> 00:21:35,100
Will you marry me?

391
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:55,740
Yes.

392
00:21:56,740 --> 00:21:58,900
Otherwise, how many more six years
do you want me to wait?

393
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,500
In a minute.

394
00:22:39,380 --> 00:22:39,860
Who is it?

395
00:22:42,580 --> 00:22:43,100
Tong?

396
00:22:44,780 --> 00:22:45,620
I found a buyer.

397
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:47,860
What?

398
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:49,780
Weilan agreed to the purchase.

399
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:52,060
They'll buy all your materials

400
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:53,580
at the agreed price,

401
00:22:54,020 --> 00:22:55,060
but payment will be made
in installments.

402
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:56,020
Really?

403
00:22:57,900 --> 00:22:58,740
That's great, Tong.

404
00:23:36,820 --> 00:23:37,620
I'm leaving.

405
00:23:39,020 --> 00:23:39,540
Tong.

406
00:23:41,540 --> 00:23:42,020
Tong.

407
00:23:42,780 --> 00:23:43,420
What's wrong?

408
00:23:43,900 --> 00:23:44,700
I'm just tired.

409
00:23:45,260 --> 00:23:46,460
How about having breakfast together
tomorrow morning?

410
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:50,740
Tong.

411
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:15,580
Ding Zhitong, you can't do this.

412
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:41,560
[Gan Yang]

413
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:49,100
Hey, Tong, what are you doing?

414
00:25:50,260 --> 00:25:51,300
Still sleeping?

415
00:25:52,420 --> 00:25:53,220
What is it?

416
00:25:53,700 --> 00:25:54,700
Just open your door.

417
00:25:55,900 --> 00:25:56,860
I'm at your doorstep.

418
00:25:57,140 --> 00:25:58,060
I made breakfast for you.

419
00:26:04,340 --> 00:26:04,900
Gan Yang.

420
00:26:12,220 --> 00:26:13,540
Let's not see each other again.

421
00:26:26,060 --> 00:26:26,820
Why?

422
00:26:26,820 --> 00:26:29,420
♪Long-lost memories come flooding back♪

423
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:30,260
What happened?

424
00:26:30,740 --> 00:26:31,580
Let's talk in person.

425
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:34,980
I'm not home.

426
00:26:36,060 --> 00:26:37,940
I have to leave Shanghai for a few days.

427
00:26:38,980 --> 00:26:39,860
Where are you now?

428
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:40,780
I'll come to you.

429
00:26:40,900 --> 00:26:41,540
No need.

430
00:26:41,540 --> 00:26:45,660
♪We longed to stay♪

431
00:26:45,660 --> 00:26:47,060
I don't have anything to talk about.

432
00:26:47,940 --> 00:26:49,220
I've said everything I wanted to say.

433
00:26:49,220 --> 00:26:53,390
♪Couldn't help but glance back
as we parted♪

434
00:26:53,860 --> 00:26:56,300
♪That tenderness we couldn't keep♪

435
00:26:56,300 --> 00:26:57,660
Then what was last night's kiss about?

436
00:27:00,540 --> 00:27:01,740
You still have feelings for me.

437
00:27:01,740 --> 00:27:04,420
♪Hidden in silence, buried deep♪

438
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:05,020
Tong.

439
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,020
What are you afraid of?

440
00:27:09,020 --> 00:27:11,900
♪Someone once gave you heart and soul♪

441
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:13,340
I've already contacted the buyer.

442
00:27:15,020 --> 00:27:16,300
You just need to handle the rest.

443
00:27:16,300 --> 00:27:20,300
♪Someone let warm times
slip from control♪

444
00:27:20,300 --> 00:27:20,900
Gan Yang.

445
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:23,420
Bye.

446
00:27:23,980 --> 00:27:24,940
Hey, Tong, don't hang up.

447
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:25,660
Hello?

448
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:28,490
♪All the courage from pain
was to let go♪

449
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:33,910
♪And to let you grow♪

450
00:27:35,840 --> 00:27:38,890
♪Someone asks me to forget♪

451
00:27:39,440 --> 00:27:42,160
♪Whenever thoughts arise♪

452
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:48,800
♪Someone once stood firm behind me♪

453
00:27:49,520 --> 00:27:55,840
♪Someone risked it all to hold me♪

454
00:27:56,200 --> 00:28:02,600
♪Now lost and found, I'm left here♪

455
00:28:03,150 --> 00:28:09,160
♪Down the roads we raced♪

456
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:12,880
♪Someone never truly erased♪

457
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:17,900
♪Every longing space♪

458
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:19,220
Don't you have your own office?

459
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:21,220
Take your snogging somewhere else.

460
00:28:21,260 --> 00:28:22,260
Like we want to be here.

461
00:28:22,580 --> 00:28:24,060
Everyone

462
00:28:24,060 --> 00:28:25,020
is packing up.

463
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:26,300
It's the only quiet place here.

464
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:33,580
What's wrong?

465
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:35,740
Didn't Ding Zhitong

466
00:28:35,740 --> 00:28:37,420
already solve the materials issue?

467
00:28:37,740 --> 00:28:38,780
What's going on between you two?

468
00:28:39,140 --> 00:28:40,300
Who am I supposed to ask?

469
00:28:41,180 --> 00:28:42,420
Haven't you two gotten back together?

470
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:44,540
You'd better hurry up.

471
00:28:44,780 --> 00:28:46,220
We're leaving for Putian soon.

472
00:28:46,380 --> 00:28:48,620
Long-distance visits
will be tough for her.

473
00:28:48,660 --> 00:28:49,820
Like I don't want to.

474
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:50,780
Really?

475
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:53,180
Ding Zhitong said no?

476
00:28:54,220 --> 00:28:55,060
That doesn't make sense.

477
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:56,100
You two were inseparable

478
00:28:56,100 --> 00:28:57,060
the other day.

479
00:28:57,540 --> 00:28:59,260
She helped you sell the materials

480
00:28:59,260 --> 00:29:00,580
and even quit the Training Box project.

481
00:29:00,620 --> 00:29:01,860
She clearly still has feelings for you.

482
00:29:02,540 --> 00:29:03,940
You all think so?

483
00:29:04,220 --> 00:29:05,740
Of course she does.

484
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:07,820
With my female intuition, absolutely.

485
00:29:08,300 --> 00:29:09,380
She has feelings for me

486
00:29:09,780 --> 00:29:11,300
but keeps pushing me away.

487
00:29:13,940 --> 00:29:14,820
What does that mean?

488
00:29:15,420 --> 00:29:15,940
No idea.

489
00:29:16,540 --> 00:29:17,980
But it makes no sense.

490
00:29:18,020 --> 00:29:19,820
You've already cleared up
the misunderstandings.

491
00:29:20,060 --> 00:29:21,460
She shouldn't be treating you like this.

492
00:29:21,620 --> 00:29:23,420
Is there something about Ding Zhitong

493
00:29:23,500 --> 00:29:24,380
you don't know?

494
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:26,780
Something I don't know...

495
00:29:32,700 --> 00:29:34,340
There must have been something
I didn't know.

496
00:29:47,300 --> 00:29:47,940
Song Mingmei.

497
00:29:49,980 --> 00:29:50,700
Gan Yang?

498
00:29:51,140 --> 00:29:51,780
What are you doing here?

499
00:29:58,100 --> 00:29:59,180
Are you sure you want to know?

500
00:30:00,380 --> 00:30:01,580
Even if it means

501
00:30:01,580 --> 00:30:02,900
you two can never be together?

502
00:30:05,100 --> 00:30:06,020
What exactly happened?

503
00:30:06,340 --> 00:30:07,420
Answer my question first.

504
00:30:13,260 --> 00:30:15,060
I know she's been suffering lately.

505
00:30:16,460 --> 00:30:18,020
But if it's because of me,

506
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:20,700
whatever it is,

507
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:25,220
I don't want her to carry it alone.

508
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,100
That attitude

509
00:30:30,060 --> 00:30:31,500
proves she didn't love the wrong man.

510
00:30:33,060 --> 00:30:34,060
Can you tell me now?

511
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:41,500
Tong made me promise not to tell you.

512
00:30:42,220 --> 00:30:43,660
If you had asked me earlier,

513
00:30:43,660 --> 00:30:44,780
I wouldn't have told you.

514
00:30:45,740 --> 00:30:47,980
But so much has happened recently.

515
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:50,340
I believe we should live in the moment.

516
00:30:54,540 --> 00:30:56,460
You never know
which will come knocking first,

517
00:30:56,460 --> 00:30:57,500
tomorrow or the tragedy.

518
00:30:58,700 --> 00:30:59,580
What do you mean?

519
00:31:00,380 --> 00:31:01,500
After you broke up,

520
00:31:02,260 --> 00:31:03,780
a lot of things happened to Tong.

521
00:31:04,500 --> 00:31:05,740
Do you know where she is now?

522
00:31:08,180 --> 00:31:08,820
No.

523
00:31:11,260 --> 00:31:12,060
She's in her hometown

524
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:15,260
visiting her mother's grave.

525
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:36,860
When did that happen?

526
00:31:39,780 --> 00:31:40,620
Remember

527
00:31:40,620 --> 00:31:42,340
when she came to Putian to find you?

528
00:31:48,420 --> 00:31:50,340
The day you broke up with her,

529
00:31:50,820 --> 00:31:52,300
her mother passed away.

530
00:31:54,580 --> 00:31:57,260
She didn't even get to see her mother
one last time.

531
00:31:58,740 --> 00:32:01,980
Losing her closest family destroyed her.

532
00:32:02,820 --> 00:32:04,340
She locked herself away,

533
00:32:04,340 --> 00:32:06,860
starving and silent for days.

534
00:32:08,780 --> 00:32:10,980
I was stuck overseas, helpless.

535
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:12,060
Feng Sheng

536
00:32:12,060 --> 00:32:14,180
was her lifeline then.

537
00:32:16,060 --> 00:32:17,980
When she fainted at home,

538
00:32:18,220 --> 00:32:19,380
he found her in time

539
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:20,820
and took her to the hospital.

540
00:32:22,020 --> 00:32:23,340
Later, she said yes to his proposal,

541
00:32:23,340 --> 00:32:24,940
out of thanks.

542
00:32:26,260 --> 00:32:29,940
But when she realized
she couldn't love him,

543
00:32:30,660 --> 00:32:32,100
she broke off the engagement

544
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,500
and left for Hong Kong, China alone.

545
00:32:36,980 --> 00:32:38,700
And you know the rest.

546
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:31,400
[In Memory of Father Ding Minghui
and Mother Lin Hechun]

547
00:33:54,900 --> 00:33:55,500
Mrs. Ding,

548
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:57,980
I'm sorry

549
00:34:02,620 --> 00:34:03,780
I only came to see you now.

550
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:09,260
Back then, I thought breaking up
with Tong...

551
00:34:14,820 --> 00:34:15,980
was for her own good.

552
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:20,700
But I didn't know so many things
had happened...

553
00:34:23,220 --> 00:34:24,620
making her blame herself...

554
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:27,420
and feel guilty until now.

555
00:34:28,940 --> 00:34:29,620
I'm sorry.

556
00:34:30,500 --> 00:34:31,340
It's all my fault.

557
00:35:01,460 --> 00:35:02,060
Tong.

558
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:04,980
I'm sorry.

559
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:06,700
Because of me,

560
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:08,740
you've endured so much these years.

561
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:15,180
On the night we split up,

562
00:35:17,420 --> 00:35:18,660
after I left yours,

563
00:35:20,220 --> 00:35:21,500
I was going to go straight home.

564
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:23,860
But it was too late

565
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:25,980
and there were no return buses.

566
00:35:28,420 --> 00:35:30,260
I had to stay in Putian for the night,

567
00:35:31,820 --> 00:35:33,660
planning to catch the first bus
the next morning.

568
00:35:37,620 --> 00:35:39,300
Then I spiked a fever.

569
00:36:04,900 --> 00:36:06,140
Hey, Mom?

570
00:36:06,860 --> 00:36:07,340
Tong!

571
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:11,260
You said you were coming home.

572
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:12,460
Why didn't you
answer the phone all night?

573
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:13,700
I was worried sick.

574
00:36:14,460 --> 00:36:15,620
I've got a fever.

575
00:36:16,620 --> 00:36:17,780
How did you get a fever?

576
00:36:18,580 --> 00:36:19,260
Where are you?

577
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:21,140
It's okay.

578
00:36:23,380 --> 00:36:24,620
I'll be home soon.

579
00:36:25,660 --> 00:36:26,220
Tong?

580
00:36:46,700 --> 00:36:47,260
Tong!

581
00:37:07,020 --> 00:37:08,700
She must have been really worried.

582
00:37:10,540 --> 00:37:12,900
She couldn't reach me
when she needed me the most.

583
00:37:15,020 --> 00:37:15,420
Mom.

584
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:18,960
I'm sorry.

585
00:37:24,620 --> 00:37:26,580
She was found by the neighbor
the next morning.

586
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:30,100
Then she was taken to the hospital.

587
00:37:31,580 --> 00:37:32,900
But when I woke up,

588
00:37:35,660 --> 00:37:37,060
it was already noon the next day.

589
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:43,780
Hey, girl,

590
00:37:44,340 --> 00:37:45,260
thank goodness you're awake.

591
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:46,940
You scared me to death.

592
00:37:47,420 --> 00:37:48,660
I thought something terrible
had happened.

593
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:49,460
Are you okay?

594
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:51,060
What's the date today?

595
00:37:51,420 --> 00:37:53,060
Well, the 13th.

596
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:55,420
You were supposed to check out
yesterday.

597
00:37:55,620 --> 00:37:56,940
I'm glad I came in to take a look.

598
00:37:57,020 --> 00:37:58,700
When I came in, I saw you fainted here.

599
00:37:59,380 --> 00:38:00,260
It scared me to death.

600
00:38:00,780 --> 00:38:01,540
Where's my phone?

601
00:38:02,620 --> 00:38:03,980
It's charging right here.

602
00:38:04,300 --> 00:38:05,980
I was going to call your family,

603
00:38:06,020 --> 00:38:07,300
but your phone was off.

604
00:38:08,140 --> 00:38:09,460
Okay, I'm glad you're awake.

605
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,460
I'll get back to work.

606
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:12,260
Remember to extend your stay later.

607
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:15,280
[Feng Sheng]

608
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:19,180
Hello?

609
00:38:19,340 --> 00:38:19,980
Ding Zhitong,

610
00:38:20,100 --> 00:38:20,700
come to the hospital now.

611
00:38:20,820 --> 00:38:21,580
Something happened to your mother.

612
00:38:32,020 --> 00:38:32,540
Tong.

613
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:35,020
Your mother...

614
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:15,780
Mom!

615
00:39:19,220 --> 00:39:20,540
Mom.

616
00:39:29,180 --> 00:39:30,580
I rushed to the hospital

617
00:39:30,620 --> 00:39:31,740
as fast as I could,

618
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:33,980
but I still didn't get to

619
00:39:35,620 --> 00:39:36,900
see her one last time.

620
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:53,380
Tong.

621
00:39:55,420 --> 00:39:56,820
I just learned all this.

622
00:39:58,660 --> 00:39:59,700
If I had been...

623
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:03,260
honest with you

624
00:40:04,500 --> 00:40:05,900
instead of breaking up with you...

625
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:11,420
none of this would have happened.

626
00:40:24,060 --> 00:40:25,140
I did blame you for a time.

627
00:40:26,180 --> 00:40:27,780
If you hadn't suddenly
broken up with me...

628
00:40:29,340 --> 00:40:30,780
none of this would have happened.

629
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,660
But then I realized

630
00:40:39,500 --> 00:40:40,140
that blaming you

631
00:40:41,660 --> 00:40:42,980
was just me avoiding the truth.

632
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:46,340
It had nothing to do with you at all.

633
00:40:49,220 --> 00:40:50,180
In the end,

634
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:52,860
it's all my fault.

635
00:41:02,180 --> 00:41:02,900
Ding Zhitong,

636
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:05,660
this wasn't on you.

637
00:41:07,660 --> 00:41:09,540
You can't keep shouldering
all the guilt.

638
00:41:10,380 --> 00:41:11,580
The year after we broke up,

639
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:14,940
I avoided everything related to you,

640
00:41:16,140 --> 00:41:17,900
afraid of triggering memories.

641
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:22,900
Until we met again later,

642
00:41:23,900 --> 00:41:26,020
I repeatedly told myself to hate you,

643
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:29,060
but I just couldn't do it.

644
00:41:31,660 --> 00:41:33,820
I also tried convincing myself
to let go of my grudges

645
00:41:34,420 --> 00:41:35,820
and give us another chance,

646
00:41:37,700 --> 00:41:39,140
but I still couldn't do it.

647
00:41:42,380 --> 00:41:44,100
So you kept this from me

648
00:41:46,580 --> 00:41:48,300
to spare me the same guilt you carried.

649
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:57,300
Tong.

650
00:41:59,820 --> 00:42:01,500
Does this mean
we really can't go back now?

651
00:42:37,080 --> 00:42:42,110
♪Long-lost memories come flooding back♪

652
00:42:43,710 --> 00:42:50,440
♪As we searched for love's missing part♪

653
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:56,790
♪We longed to stay♪

654
00:42:57,300 --> 00:43:03,140
♪Couldn't help but glance back
as we parted♪

655
00:43:04,460 --> 00:43:10,540
♪That tenderness we couldn't keep♪

656
00:43:11,190 --> 00:43:17,190
♪Hidden in silence, buried deep♪

657
00:43:17,990 --> 00:43:24,590
♪Someone once gave you heart and soul♪

658
00:43:25,160 --> 00:43:31,640
♪Someone let warm times
slip from control♪

659
00:43:32,260 --> 00:43:38,810
♪All the courage from pain
was to let go♪

660
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:45,040
♪And to let you grow♪

661
00:43:46,190 --> 00:43:52,260
♪Someone asks me to forget,
whenever thoughts arise♪

662
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:59,860
♪Someone once stood firm behind me♪

663
00:44:00,120 --> 00:44:06,690
♪Someone risked it all to hold me♪

664
00:44:07,010 --> 00:44:13,260
♪Now lost and found, I'm left here♪

665
00:44:13,760 --> 00:44:19,810
♪Down the roads we raced♪

666
00:44:20,740 --> 00:44:33,340
♪Someone never truly erased
every longing space♪
